) that presumably exerted selection pressure on 
<taxonomicName box="[1017,1153,655,680]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Eriotheca" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="52" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="saxicola">
<emphasis box="[1017,1153,655,680]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="52">E. saxicola</emphasis>
